title: Dirty Dancing: Havana Zeits 8/2: Russell Westbrook, Lindsey Graham, DaBaby, Rick Flair, Lovers and Friends, Simone Biles
itunes:title: Dirty Dancing: Havana Zeits 8/2: Russell Westbrook, Lindsey Graham, DaBaby, Rick Flair, Lovers and Friends, Simone Biles
description:
In this edition of Dirty Dancing: Havana Zeits, Miles and special guest host Jacquis Neal discuss Russell Westbrook getting signed to the Lakers, Lindsey Graham getting COVID, DaBaby "apologizing" for his homophobic remarks, "The Nature Boy" Rick Flair FINALLY being released from WWE, the 'Lovers and Friends' festival, and Simone Biles rejoining the Olympics Competition
